{"tid":2427986,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳日本政府醞釀向窮困人士額外派錢","createTime":"2021-03-01T08:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T08:44:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a855abc6ec2505241ac01dc23dd0610d584529e2","tid":2427986,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T08:21:24.000Z","msg":"《路透》引述消息報道，日本政府及執政黨官員正討論向低收入家庭額外派錢，以協助度過新冠危機。報道指額外派錢金額未定，但將必然遠少於早前全民派錢的10萬日圓(940美元)金額。日本政府上次派錢共動用12.9萬億日圓(1,200億美元)，由發債支付。<br />\n<br />\n部分執政黨議員關注職位流失及自殺問題，早前提出向窮困人士額外派錢每人10萬日圓，並提出支援託兒及提供食米及其他糧食。消息指日本政府及執政聯盟計劃在下財年預算案通過後，再整合新的經濟措施。日本財政大臣麻生太郎一直抗拒推出新開支計劃，認為應先批准預算案，並在需要時動用緊急儲備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.1079384/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.1079384%2F2&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3SDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=289572ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.1079384/2</a>"},{"pid":"5b2e67ee2305b3b09d82c39bb8b75e7822a67a2f","tid":2427986,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T08:27:51.000Z","msg":"東奧如果搞唔成，成個日本gg<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a6041407d254813b401b4075c091215c573c80","tid":2427986,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T08:30:20.000Z","msg":"日本窮人慘D定香港窮人慘D"},{"pid":"9804f1a2de534b02edca90a40d7a4b8058dfce75","tid":2427986,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4a6041407d254813b401b4075c091215c573c80","tid":2427986,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T08:30:20.000Z","msg":"日本窮人慘D定香港窮人慘D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T08:43:59.000Z","msg":"日本政府會給市民所急"},{"pid":"5e9e5aa06a373e2051077df0e2b4a5b6141307ed","tid":2427986,"uid":187709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b2e67ee2305b3b09d82c39bb8b75e7822a67a2f","tid":2427986,"uid":52594,"lik